    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Wed Mar 18 10:00:00 CST 2026] 陈静你好，关于张涛的事情。我已经给他发了3次书面警告了，PIP也做了，该做的都做了。他绩效确实不行——Q3两个项目延期，Q4代码质量问题被客户投诉。我给了他足够的机会。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031802000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0000",
        "seq": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Noted Sun Wei's account. He claims:\n- 3 written warnings issued to Zhang Tao\n- PIP completed\n- Performance issues are substantive: Q3 project delays, Q4 code quality complaints\n\n**Verification needed:** Cross-reference \"3 written warnings\" against pip-email-chain.md. The email system should show the actual count of formal warning emails sent."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031802010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0001",
        "seq": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Wed Mar 18 14:00:00 CST 2026] PIP我2月1号就发了邮件通知张涛。2月15号做了Week 2 check-in，也发了邮件。3月4号做了最后一次review，面谈的。之后综合评估他没达标，3月13号正式辞退。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031806000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0002",
        "seq": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Sun Wei's PIP timeline account:\n- Feb 1: PIP initiation email sent ✓ (confirmed in pip-email-chain.md)\n- Feb 15: Week 2 check-in via email ✓ (confirmed in pip-email-chain.md)\n- Mar 4: Week 4 review -- **\"face-to-face meeting\"** (no email documentation found)\n- Mar 13: Termination\n\n**Key gap:** The March 4 check-in was conducted verbally (\"面谈\") without email documentation. The PIP email chain shows only the Feb 15 check-in email. The company PIP policy requires documented check-ins at regular intervals."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031806010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0003",
        "seq": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Thu Mar 19 09:00:00 CST 2026] 我要说明一下张涛的具体绩效问题。Q3的用户认证模块延期了3周，导致客户端发版推迟。Q4他负责的支付接口有两个P2级别bug进入production。代码review通过率只有60%，团队平均85%。这些都有记录。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031901000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0004",
        "seq": 5
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Sun Wei provides specific performance data:\n\n**Zhang Tao's Performance Issues:**\n- Q3 2025: User authentication module delayed 3 weeks → client release postponed\n- Q4 2025: 2 P2-level bugs in payment interface reached production\n- Code review pass rate: 60% (team average: 85%)\n\n**Assessment:** These are substantive performance concerns supported by the HR file's performance ratings (Q3: Below Expectations, Q4: Needs Improvement). The performance problems appear genuine regardless of whether the termination process was properly followed. The question is process compliance, not performance substance."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031901010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0005",
        "seq": 6
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Thu Mar 19 14:00:00 CST 2026] 陈浩可以确认，我跟他沟通过整个过程。每次警告之后我都跟他说了。12月的时候我还跟陈浩说'再不行就要PIP了'。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031906000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0006",
        "seq": 7
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Sun Wei references Chen Hao as a corroborating witness. Cross-referencing with the Chen Hao Feishu session:\n\n**Alignment check:**\n- Sun Wei says he communicated each warning to Chen Hao ✓ (Chen Hao confirms Sun Wei reported \"3 warnings\")\n- Sun Wei mentioned escalation to PIP in December ✓ (consistent with timeline)\n\n**However:** Chen Hao Feishu Loop 3 reveals he \"没有一封封去查\" (did not verify each warning email individually). Chen Hao corroborates that Sun Wei *reported* 3 warnings, but did not independently verify they were *documented* as written warnings in the email system."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026031906010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0007",
        "seq": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Fri Mar 20 09:00:00 CST 2026] 张涛走了以后团队的项目进度还好，我临时把他的任务分给了李明和赵亮。但长期看还是需要招一个人补位。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032001000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0008",
        "seq": 9
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Team continuity after Zhang Tao's departure is noted. The immediate workload distribution to Li Ming and Zhao Liang appears manageable in the short term. Backfill planning can be discussed separately. Let's stay focused on the investigation for now."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032001010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0009",
        "seq": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Fri Mar 20 14:00:00 CST 2026] 想请教一下，backfill的JD什么时候可以发出去？我希望尽快开始招聘流程。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032006000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0010",
        "seq": 11
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The backfill JD timeline depends on the outcome of the wrongful termination investigation. If the investigation finds process gaps, the company may need to consider remediation options before proceeding with a replacement hire. I recommend waiting until the investigation is complete before posting the JD."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032006010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0011",
        "seq": 12
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Mon Mar 23 09:00:00 CST 2026] 这个季度的performance calibration我们准备在4月初做。除了张涛，团队整体表现还是不错的，特别是李明在Q1的表现很突出。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032301000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0012",
        "seq": 13
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Performance calibration planning is noted. For the current investigation, I may need to reference team performance benchmarks to contextualize Zhang Tao's metrics. The 85% code review pass rate team average is one such benchmark already documented."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032301010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0013",
        "seq": 14
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "[Email 孙伟 Mon Mar 23 14:00:00 CST 2026] 我们Q1的工程目标基本都按计划完成了。系统可用性99.9%，部署频率也提升了。整体看团队在好的方向发展。"
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032306000,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0014",
        "seq": 15
      }
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Q1 engineering KPIs look healthy. These broader team metrics provide context: the team is performing well overall, which makes the decision to terminate an underperformer understandable from a management perspective. The investigation question remains whether the *process* was correctly followed, not whether the *decision* was reasonable."
        }
      ],
      "timestamp": 2026032306010,
      "__openclaw": {
        "id": "msg0015",
        "seq": 16
      }
    }
  ],
